ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
SubjectBARLEY - 2010 (Feb-July) UNSOLD STOCK ** Transfer to 2010-2011 Pool Accounts **
PrecisAuthority for THE CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD to transfer the BARLEY unsold from the preceding pool that began on February 1, 2010, and ended on July 31, 2010, to the current pool period that began on August 1, 2010, and will end on January 31, 2011.
